*   slide
*   bend
*   vibrato
*   hammer-on
*   pull-off
*   harmonic
*   muted / percussive hit

2025 年已有 guitar-specific 数据集和系统把 technique-aware transcription 当成重点方向，说明这会是明显的差异化能力。[arXiv+1](https://arxiv.org/abs/2510.02597?utm_source=chatgpt.com)

