### D. Motion / Handoff Master

分类总表：
- Scene Entry
- Scene Exit
- Shared Handoff
- Focus Migration
- Runtime Overlay Motion
- Trainer → Core
- Core → Ecosystem
- Closing Exit

必须优先直接接入的来源：
- Motion `AnimatePresence`
- Motion `LayoutGroup`
